    ],
    "text": "On the night of 28.02.2026, a team of officers from the Airport Unit of the Police Narcotics Bureau conducted a raid at the arrival terminal of the airport and arrested a suspect with 36,000 cigarettes (180 cartons) illegally brought into the country.",
