    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      638.37,
      526.05,
      665.45
    ],
    "text": "Two suspects arrested with a stock of vegetable seeds illegally brought into the country - Negombo Divisional Criminal Investigation Bureau.",
    "fonts": [
